data.description: Gorgeous! Welcome to this cozy home nestled in a community that is so unique! When walking up to the home, you'll first fall in love with the adorable front porch and lush landscaping. This Neal Communities "Glory 2" model offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms PLUS a DEN that could be a 4th bedroom or office. The spacious split open floor plan boasts immaculate upgrades such as updated laminate flooring, plantation shutters, crown molding, 42-inch cabinets and stainless steel appliances that make this home just perfect! The private Master suite offers dual sinks, walk-in closet, and stand-up shower! The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms are very spacious on the split end of the home and have their own private bath. Sliding doors lead to your private screened lanai with a preserve view. Forest Creek has wonderful amenities! Clubhouse, fitness, swimming pool, playground, and an 18 acre lake that is great for kayaks, canoes and fishing. Sidewalks throughout community are great for strolling around the lake or sitting and watching wildlife from the lakeside gazebo. Zoned for the new PARRISH HIGH SCHOOL! Conveniently located close to mall, restaurants, golf, shopping and beaches. The Fort Hamer bridge makes for easy commuting to Lakewood Ranch. HOA only $27.50/quarter.
